ZH: 房东要求每月按时交房租。
EN: The landlord requires payment of rent on time every month.

ZH: 房东正在整修房屋。
EN: The landlord is renovating the house.

ZH: 我和房东签订了一份租赁合同。
EN: I signed a lease agreement with the landlord.

ZH: 我的房东很友善。
EN: My landlord is very friendly.

ZH: 我给房东打了一个电话。
EN: I called the landlord.

ZH: 我和房东沟通了一下。
EN: I communicated with the landlord.

ZH: 房东让我照顾好房子。
EN: The landlord asked me to take good care of the house.

ZH: 房东说他会尽快修理漏水的水管。
EN: The landlord said he would fix the leaking pipe as soon as possible.

ZH: 房东要求我不要养宠物。
EN: The landlord asked me not to have pets.

ZH: 我的房东很容易相处。
EN: My landlord is easy to get along with.

ZH: 房东提醒我及时交付水电费。
EN: The landlord reminded me to pay utilities on time.

ZH: 房东拒绝了我的续租请求。
EN: The landlord rejected my lease renewal request.

ZH: 房东告诉我他要出售房屋。
EN: The landlord told me he is selling the house.

ZH: 房东不允许我在房子里吸烟。
EN: The landlord does not allow smoking in the house.

ZH: 房东每月都会来检查房子。
EN: The landlord comes to inspect the house every month.

ZH: 房东要求我保持房屋整洁。
EN: The landlord asked me to keep the house clean.

ZH: 房东对我很有耐心。
EN: The landlord is very patient with me.

ZH: 我们的房东是一位老太太。
EN: Our landlord is an elderly lady.

ZH: 房东给了我一份很偏僻的地段。
EN: The landlord gave me a very remote location.

ZH: 房东不允许我改装房屋。
EN: The landlord does not allow me to renovate the house.
